kid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\"}, {\"begin\": 456, \"end\": 459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Environmental_Protection_Agency\", \"score\": 0.9999927956619411, \"rank\": 7.20359780998762e-06, \"text\": \"EPA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Environmental_Protection_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Environmental_Protection_Agency\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian swimming, boxing, hockey and basketball fans will have reason to be watching overnight, while the men's skateboarding heats will finally start after a two-delay delay because of rain.\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 751, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 557, \"end\": 576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian swimming\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's what's happening on day three.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The women's 200m freestyle final is shaping up as the mother of all club meets between training partners Ariarne Titmus and Mollie O'Callaghan.\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariarne Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\"}, {\"begin\": 916, \"end\": 934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mollie O'Callaghan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Titmus broke O'Callaghan's world record six weeks ago.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 936, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Titmus and O'Callaghan both cruised into Monday night's 200m freestyle final as the top-two qualifiers.\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 992, \"end\": 998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Titmus won narrowly ahead of O'Callaghan but said the result wasn't significant.\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1097, \"end\": 1103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You always want to be in the middle of the pool in a final and get yourself in a good position,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But that was really the only plan for tonight, I tried to conserve as much as I could.\\\"\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Titmus touched in one minute 54.64 seconds, six-hundredths of a second quicker than O'Callaghan.\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1378, \"end\": 1384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Max Giuliani will be competing in the men's 200m freestyle final.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1476, \"end\": 1479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9994267731229274, \"rank\": 0.000517758412976254, \"text\": \"Max\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Cunningham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic debutant was fifth-fastest in the semis to reach the final.\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile Ella Ramsay and Jenna Forrester will compete in the women's individual medley final.\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1642, \"end\": 1647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenna_Bush_Hager\", \"score\": 0.5242936469510509, \"rank\": 0.5285642955734795, \"text\": \"Jenna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenna_Bush_Hager\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenna_Bush_Hager\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World individual champion Cassiel Rousseau will combine with Domonic Bedggood in the 10m synchronised platform, with British flag bearer Tom Daley and Noah Williams also competing.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1892, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1738, \"end\": 1745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cassiel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cassiel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cassiel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cassiel\"}, {\"begin\": 1746, \"end\": 1754, \"ti